cast.overview: As America's stock of athletic young men is depleted during World War II, a professional all-female baseball league springs up in the Midwest, funded by publicity-hungry candy maker Walter Harvey. Competitive sisters Dottie Hinson and Kit Keller spar with each other, scout Ernie Capadino and grumpy has-been coach Jimmy Dugan on their way to fame.
cast.title: A League of Their Own

details.biography: Anne Ramsay is an American stage, film and television actress, writer and director, best known for playing Lisa Stemple on the television comedy show "Mad About You". She holds a BA in Theater from the University of California, Los Angeles, USA.
details.name: Anne Ramsay
